### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST SHIFTS API - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@managerToken = 
@cashierToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN (Chạy trước để lấy token)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Manager
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager",
  "password": "Manager@123"
}

### 1.3 Login Cashier
# @name loginCashier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "cashier",
  "password": "Cashier@123"
}

### ============================================
### 📋 2. GET ALL SHIFTS
### ============================================

### 2.1 Admin - Get All Shifts (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.2 Admin - Get Shifts with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.3 Admin - Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts?status=OPEN
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.4 Admin - Filter by Cashier
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts?cashierId=3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.5 Admin - Filter by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.6 Cashier - Get Shifts (chỉ thấy ca của mình) (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 2.7 No Token - Get Shifts (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts

### ============================================
### 🔍 3. GET SHIFT BY ID
### ============================================

### 3.1 Admin - Get Shift by ID (Expected: 200 OK or 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Cashier - Get Own Shift (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 3.3 Cashier - Get Other's Shift (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/2
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 3.4 Admin - Get Non-existent Shift (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ⏱️ 4. GET CURRENT SHIFT
### ============================================

### 4.1 Cashier - Get Current Open Shift (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/current
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 4.2 Admin - Get Current Shift (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/current
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 🟢 5. OPEN SHIFT
### ============================================

### 5.1 Cashier - Open Shift (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/open
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "openingCash": 500000,
  "note": "Ca làm việc buổi sáng"
}

### 5.2 Cashier - Open Shift with Zero Cash (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/open
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "openingCash": 0
}

### 5.3 Cashier - Open Shift when Already Open (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/open
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "openingCash": 1000000
}

### 5.4 No Token - Open Shift (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/open
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "openingCash": 500000
}

### ============================================
### 🔴 6. CLOSE SHIFT
### ============================================

### 6.1 Cashier - Close Shift (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/1/close
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "closingCash": 2500000,
  "note": "Doanh thu ca sáng tốt"
}

### 6.2 Cashier - Close Other's Shift (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/2/close
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "closingCash": 1000000
}

### 6.3 Admin - Close Any Shift (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/3/close
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "closingCash": 3000000
}

### 6.4 Cashier - Close Already Closed Shift (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/1/close
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "closingCash": 1000000
}

### 6.5 Cashier - Close Non-existent Shift (Expected: 404 Not Found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/99999/close
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "closingCash": 1000000
}

### ============================================
### ✏️ 7. UPDATE SHIFT
### ============================================

### 7.1 Admin - Update Shift Note (Expected: 200 OK)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "note": "Ghi chú đã cập nhật bởi Admin"
}

### 7.2 Cashier - Update Own Shift (Expected: 200 OK)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "note": "Ghi chú cập nhật bởi Cashier"
}

### 7.3 Cashier - Update Other's Shift (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "note": "Không được phép"
}

### 7.4 Admin - Update Non-existent Shift (Expected: 404 Not Found)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "note": "Test"
}

### ============================================
### 📊 8. GET SHIFT REPORT
### ============================================

### 8.1 Admin - Get Shift Report (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/1/report
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.2 Cashier - Get Own Shift Report (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/1/report
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 8.3 Cashier - Get Other's Shift Report (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/2/report
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 8.4 Admin - Get Non-existent Shift Report (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shifts/99999/report
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Chạy các request Login đầu tiên để lấy token
### 3. Copy token vào biến tương ứng
### 4. Chạy các request test theo thứ tự
###
### WORKFLOW TEST:
### 1. Open Shift → 2. Get Current Shift → 3. Close Shift
### 4. Get Shift Report
###
