### [ ] Open shift with zero → 200 OK
### [ ] Open when already open → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] No token → 401 Unauthorized
###
### CLOSE SHIFT:
### [ ] Close own shift → 200 OK
### [ ] Close other's shift (Cashier) → 403 Forbidden
### [ ] Admin close any shift → 200 OK
### [ ] Close already closed → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Close non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### UPDATE:
### [ ] Admin update any shift → 200 OK
### [ ] Cashier update own shift → 200 OK
### [ ] Cashier update other's → 403 Forbidden
### [ ] Update non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### SHIFT REPORT:
